title: Grateful Dead Live at Shoreline Amphitheatre on 1987-10-04
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, When Push Comes To Shove, Walkin' Blues, High Time, Desolation Row, Iko Iko

Set 2

Hell In A Bucket, Devil With The Blue Dress-> Good Golly Miss Molly-> Devil With The Blue Dress, Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Jam-> I Need A Miracle-> Dear Mr. Fantasy-> Wharf Rat-> Not Fade Away, E:Touch Of Gray-> E: Brokedown Palace
